              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43579369-kevin-ansbro?shelf=indian-fiction">indian-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43579369-kevin-ansbro?shelf=escapism">escapism</a>, 
