<span id="freeTextContainer13777450476070582689">I am undecided as to award this book with fours stars or three. <br/>It&apos;s a surreal story with some unforgettable characters. <br/><br/>It was surely worth the ride but I must confess that during the first hundred pages I was ready to shamelessly chuck it aside. I am glad I didn&apos;t. This is a story that&apos;ll stick with me for quite a while. <br/><br/>Ok...... 4 stars</span>
  <span id="freeText13777450476070582689" style="display:none">I am undecided as to award this book with fours stars or three. <br />It's a surreal story with some unforgettable characters. <br /><br />It was surely worth the ride but I must confess that during the first hundred pages I was ready to shamelessly chuck it aside. I am glad I didn't. This is a story that'll stick with me for quite a while. <br /><br />Ok...... 4 stars</span>
