              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6628596986251646345">I reread this book many years following my Pakistan encounters. It is one beautiful, philosophical, political, fantastical story in a land built on a myth. A great book to read for people from both sides of one subcontinent, and for those in love with it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review550885083">
