<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/124432.White_Mughals"><img alt="White Mughals: Love and Betrayal in Eighteenth-Century India" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1309285574l/124432._SX98_.jpg" />
